WEBVTT

13:47.899 --> 13:49.983
And now you want to
play it everywhere!

13:50.066 --> 13:51.899
Why not screen it
in the town hall too?

13:51.941 --> 13:54.858
Hey! I'll talk to those
distributors again.

13:54.899 --> 13:56.582
Talking to them isn't enough.
You have to make it happen.

13:56.691 --> 13:59.108
Anyway, I'm expecting a favourable
decision from you, Georgekutty.
